data.description: Discover elevated living in this stunning 2nd-level 2 bed/2 bath condo nestled in the sought-after area of Lake Mary. As you step inside, be greeted by vaulted ceilings and an inviting open floorplan bathed in natural light. The spacious rooms offer comfort, with the 2nd bedroom featuring French doors and an attached bath, plus the convenience of laundry facilities within. The kitchen boasts sleek black appliances, a beautiful backsplash, and wood cabinets. Enjoy the perks of the community, including a refreshing pool and access to the Seminole County school district. With just a stroll away there a Top Golf location, Cross Seminole Trails, Lake Mary YMCA, conveniently located close to everything, shopping,dining,entertainment, top-rated Seminole County schools. Just a short walk across to one of Lake Mary's waterfront restaurants known for ''The Best Hot Wings'' and live music and easy access to I-4/417,this home is perfectly situated. Schedule a showing and say hello to your new home!
